<a:ge_pink_arrow:780853910343516161> **Welcome!**

<a:ab_exclemation:780845105443373079> You can join the order for some cheap af ubisoft games <a:ab_exclemation:780845105443373079>

<a:ge_pink_arrow:780853910343516161> **Orders**
Orders will be taken until 26. Nov 2020 (end of day)!
To order see the `giraffa ordercmds` section below

<a:ge_pink_arrow:780853910343516161> **Delivery**
Games will be delivered to ubi studio DÃ¼ssledorf and will be distributed manually!

<a:ge_pink_arrow:780853910343516161> **Payment**
